data.title: I’m Going to Tell You a Secret in the UK and Canada

data.text:
According to Warner, the tentative release date of “I’m Going to Tell You a Secret” on DVD is Monday, June 19 in the UK, and Tuesday, June 20 in Canada.

As reported here yesterday, the Italian release is set to Friday, June 16, as it usual happens for those countries that have music release street dates on Fridays.
